{"tid":1955572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 受反修例事件影響警察總部需花費104萬維修","createTime":"2020-04-02T14:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T14:45:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69d9f8dceea5c584ec1c4758c16a48f3a4403a08","tid":1955572,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:28:53.000Z","msg":"反修例風波中政府建築物維修費共要6120萬元<br />\n02.04.2020 22:16<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局表示，去年反修例風波中，多幢政府建築物受到破壞，合共建築維修工程要約6120萬元。當局回覆議員就財政預算案質詢時表示，立法會大樓維修費要1530萬元，是多個建築物中最高，其次是長沙灣政府合署和政府總部，分別要930萬元和900萬元。至於警察總部，維修費要104萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278405&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278405%26csid%3D261_341&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=b836b7b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278405&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"befa4e3c011df54c4786f17ce0b3d8a25a21a589","tid":1955572,"uid":183576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 直接保育左佢列入古蹟咪得囉<br />\n增加歷史底蘊又解決警隊問題 雙贏"},{"pid":"7dda24e647ac0bb399fb2cfade25c5d9600356db","tid":1955572,"uid":225101,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"又打算用50萬買舊檀香木啊？"},{"pid":"7a92f7f8ad2513b4b9767a2b8e06d8ec22264ac6","tid":1955572,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"比黑警加人工買玩具嗰二百幾億拎去維修<br />\n夠比人爆多幾百次政府建築物洩憤<br />\n抵玩好多"},{"pid":"8e59e5f5cb0744a4ba75c9d8d407f285b915a8d1","tid":1955572,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"100萬咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69897f1fbe795a29cc90a770b9d20b0824197df","tid":1955572,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>立法會大樓維修費要1530萬元</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前唔係吹到成半億㗎咩<br />\n<br />\n立法會大樓7月1日受到示威者衝擊後，一度完全封閉以待復修。立法會早前宣佈下周三(16日)復會。身兼立法會行管會主席的立法會主席梁君彥今日表示，立法會預計能按照目標於10月16日復會，其他服務亦會陸續恢復正常。他透露，估計維修費用約<span style=\"color: red;\">4000萬元</span>。"}]}